<p class=" font-fam3 suphead">Making a Hall</p>

<p class=" tuta">Navigate to the editor, select a photo and use the <%= image_tag('text.jpg', :class => "textimg") %> icon to write your text. </p>
</div>
<div class="supimgdiv"><%= image_tag('hr19.jpg', :class => "tutimg") %></div>	
