<div class="container tut font-fam1">
<p class="font-fam3 tuth2">Editing</p>	
<p class="tuta">Change your font text to white by editing the foreground. You can also align your text with the <%= image_tag('align.jpg', :class => "exportimg") %> icon or position your text by dragging the textbox. </p>
<div class="supimgdiv"><%= image_tag('hr10.png', :class => "tutimg2") %></div>
<br /><br />

<p class="font-fam3 tuth2">Saving</p>	
<p class="tuta">Use <%= image_tag('export.jpg', :class => "exportimg") %> to save your hall. (Safari users should hold image down after export to save hall then navigate back to editor). Scroll down and select next. </p> 
<br /><br />

<p class="font-fam3 tuth2">Frequent issues</p>
<p class=" tuta">If you have trouble scrolling the editor, swipe from the head or base and scroll.</p>	
<p class=" tuta">Notice your text is truncated? leave a space above text in the textbox as seen above.</p>
<br /><br />

</div>


